data.description: Talk about a lot of room!  This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath house sits on a full acre of peace and quiet in Panther Heights in Crowley.  The entire neighborhood are 1 acre lots so there is plenty of elbow room between you and your neighbors. Walking in, you will notice the large, open concept living and kitchen space, wood flooring and cozy, brick fireplace.  The kitchen is large and open with tons of counter space, oak cabinets and gas range. Formal dining joins the kitchen but it could also be used as a home office  The master bedroom is comfortable and roomy and sports a large master bath with oversized shower and walk-in closet and oak cabinets.  Check out the covered back patio!  Your soon-to-be Oasis awaits as there is SO MUCH fun to be had here. Bring friends and family together on fall evenings and grill a few burgers during the Cowboy game.  For those hot, Texas summers, you can take a refreshing swim in the pool.  It's a must-see AND a must-have home! Minutes from CTP and DT FtWorth.
